item.title: CVE-2021-22557|2024-08-03T18:44:14.145Z -- google%20llc -- slo%20generator
item.description: SLO generator allows for loading of YAML files that if crafted in a specific format can allow for code execution within the context of the SLO Generator. We recommend upgrading SLO Generator past https://github.com/google/slo-generator/pull/173
